Line 164: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/router -run TestSessionManager` to verify session management works correctly\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/design.md:\n  Line 248: The router uses the `store.Store` interface for caching session data:\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/handler_test.go:\n  Line 63: \trouter.GET(\"/v1/sessions/:sessionId\", h.GetSession)\n  Line 64: \trouter.DELETE(\"/v1/sessions/:sessionId\", h.DeleteSession)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/integrations/spec.md:\n  Line 59: - **THEN** the schema SHALL require string parameters `router_url` and `workload_manager_url`, SHALL offer optional `language` as a select among `python`, `javascript`, and `typescript`, and SHALL allow optional `code`, `command`, `session_id`, `session_reuse` (boolean), and `code_interpreter_id`, each documented for human and LLM-oriented forms\n  Line 95: The system SHALL implement `execute` with parameters for router and workload manager URLs, optional language, session controls, and code or command execution, delegating to `agentcube.CodeInterpreterClient`.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/python-sdk/design.md:\n  Line 50: | `CodeInterpreterClient` | `router_url` ← arg or `ROUTER_URL` (required); `workload_manager_url` / `auth_token` passed to `ControlPlaneClient`; `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `verbose`, `session_id` |\n  Line 86: **Fields set on instance:** `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `verbose`, `logger`, `cp_client`, `router_url`, `session_id`, `dp_client`.\n  Line 111: **Fields:** `agent_name`, `namespace`, `timeout`, `connect_timeout`, `logger`, `router_url`, `session_id`, `dp_client`.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_2